trans-unit.source: Provides a base implementation for a ComponentEditorPage.
trans-unit.target: Har en base implementering for en ComponentEditorPage.

trans-unit.source: The ComponentEditorPage class is a complete implementation for a component editor page that consists of an empty window.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ComponentEditorPage er en komplett implementering for en komponent redigeringsprogrammet side som består av et tomt vindu.

trans-unit.source: You can extend this page to add your own controls.
trans-unit.target: Du kan utvide denne siden for å legge til egne kontroller.

trans-unit.source: ComponentEditorPage is used by a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorForm> of a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.WindowsFormsComponentEditor>.
trans-unit.target: ComponentEditorPage brukes av en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorForm>av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.WindowsFormsComponentEditor>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.WindowsFormsComponentEditor> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorForm>

trans-unit.source: Increments the loading counter.
trans-unit.target: Øker telleren innlasting.

trans-unit.source: Each procedure that performs loading or initialization should first call the EnterLoadingMode method to indicate that it will load something before the editor can display the loaded editor page.
trans-unit.target: Hver prosedyre som utfører innlasting eller initialisering må først kalle metoden EnterLoadingMode for å angi at den lastes noe før redigeringsprogrammet kan vise siden lastes inn redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: When a loading procedure that called EnterLoadingMode completes, it should call the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.ExitLoadingMode%2A> method to indicate that its part of the load process is completed.
trans-unit.target: Når en innlasting prosedyre som kalles EnterLoadingMode er fullført, må den kalle den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.ExitLoadingMode%2A>metode for å angi at del av prosessen med load er fullført.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.ExitLoadingMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.Loading%2A> property is used as a counter to determine when loading is complete.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.Loading%2A>egenskapen brukes som en teller til å bestemme når nedlastingen er fullført.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.Loading%2A>

trans-unit.source: A page is in loading mode if the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.Loading%2A> property is non-zero.
trans-unit.target: En side er under nedlastingen av modus hvis verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.Loading%2A>egenskapen er null.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentEditorPage.Loading%2A>

trans-unit.source: Processes messages that could be handled by the page.
trans-unit.target: Behandler meldinger som kan behandles av siden.

trans-unit.source: This method gives the page a chance to process messages before the caller uses them.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden gir siden mulighet til å behandle meldinger før oppkalleren bruker dem.

trans-unit.source: If this returns `true`, the message will be consumed; otherwise, the caller will continue to process the message.
trans-unit.target: Hvis dette returnerer `true`meldingen blir brukt; ellers, oppkalleren fortsetter å behandle meldingen.

trans-unit.source: The message to process.
trans-unit.target: Meldingen som skal behandles.

trans-unit.source: Loads the component into the page user interface (UI).
trans-unit.target: Laster inn komponenten i side-brukergrensesnittet (UI).

trans-unit.source: Indicates how many load dependencies remain until loading has been completed.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvor mange load avhengigheter forbli før innlasting er fullført.

trans-unit.source: This property is used to track the number of loading stages remaining.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen brukes til å spore antallet innlasting faser gjenværende.

trans-unit.source: For each process needed to completely load the document, this counter is incremented before loading begins, and decremented when each loading process completes.
trans-unit.target: Denne telleren økes for hver prosess som kreves for å laste fullstendig dokumentet, før innlasting starter, og hoppgrensen senkes når hver innlasting behandle er fullført.

trans-unit.source: The number of remaining load dependencies.
trans-unit.target: Antall gjenværende load avhengigheter.

trans-unit.source: The Help system calls the ShowHelp method to provide Help for the page.
trans-unit.target: Hjelp kaller metoden ShowHelp for å gi hjelp for siden.

trans-unit.source: ShowHelp is usually called in response to F1 or when the Help button is clicked to allow the page to bring up its associated Help topic.
